# History

### v0.2 (2017-04-08)
- Add '-rN' and '--rolls=N', for specifying how many times to roll the dice
   before exiting.
- Remove '-1' and '--once'.
- Add '-q'/'--quiet' and '-l'/'--loud'/'--verbose', for specifying how user-
   friendly the output should be. (useful for shell piping)
- Output prompt '>>> ' in interactive mode.
- Replace scons with make.

### v0.1 (2016-07-22)
- Pad spaces before dice rolls so that output is always aligned in columns.
